data.description: GORGEOUS 5 bedroom, 3 bath, 3 car garage home with POOL & OWNED SOLAR PANELS FOR HUGE SAVINGS!!! This beautiful two story is conveniently located in the Brookstone community of Providence. Home features a grand entrance with formal living area & cathedral ceilings! LARGE kitchen with island, upgraded 42" cabinets, bar area with wine rack, double ovens & ALL Stainless steel appliances! Family and dining area off of kitchen with plenty of space. FULL Bedroom and 3/4 bath downstairs! Upstairs with loft that overlooks downstairs area, UPGRADED iron stair rail, HUGE primary bedroom with LARGE bath and walk-in closet. 3 more good size bedrooms upstairs all with walk-in closets. GREAT backyard that features patio area, paver stones, Pool, artificial grass, and fire-pit area with planter box. MUST SEE!
